I don't like the distribution of the facility, you don't have line of sight for the whole area, there are many doors that are not under control. The entrance/exit doors are high and a child can go under, when I was there, nobody was watching. And in a party event, the time when you are able to get the party room, it's not even close the one reserved in advance...kids are kids and they enjoy the facilities...

Good entertainment for children. Parent's lounge is available inside and outside the Parc. Crowded on Sundays. A small reduction in entry fee until 12 noon. Grab some fruits, so that children don't crave for the junk food sold in here.
Love this soft play. The kids can play for hours on end. The place is kept clean and the staff are friendly.
